mixin borderDoc
  p The classes are named using the format 
    code border-{side}
    |  for 
    code xs
    |  and 
    code border-{breakpoint}-{side}
    |  for 
    code sm
    | , 
    code md
    | , 
    code lg
    | , and 
    code xl
    | .
  p
    | Where 
    em side
    |  is one of: 
  ul
    li
      code top
      |  - for classes that set style for 
      code border-top
    li
      code bottom
      |  - for classes that set style for 
      code border-bottom
    li
      code left
      |  - for classes that set style for 
      code border-left
    li
      code right
      |  - for classes that set style for 
      code margin-right
    li
      code x
      |  - for classes that set both 
      code *-left
      |  and 
      code *-right
    li
      code y
      |  - for classes that set both 
      code *-top
      |  and 
      code *-bottom
    li
      | blank - for classes that set the 
      code border
      |  style on all 4 side of the element.

  p.mb-0 Use border utilities to quickly style the 
    code border
    |  of an element. Great for images, buttons, or any other element.

mixin borderAdditive
